{
  "stem": "7546.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Outhouses had a certain value, because human waste was collected into large barrels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Each barrel was approximately 50 feet long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "50 feet long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were made specially for human waste.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the ghetto, we called it [? fecalia. ?] And that human waste was taken out of the ghetto for the Polish farmers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that barrel was on four wheels, and humans were dragging that barrel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of a sudden, we see a few barrels coming, and then-- by the way, they were tied in to the wagons just like horses were.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were six in the front and two in the back, pushing it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And six were dragging it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those barrels came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those people that worked these barrels were told to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they put those officers, in their uniforms, with their medals into those leather straps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they made them drag those wagons into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the women, immediately, the Germans tore off their coats, tore their hats off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The women were pushed and beaten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they went into a place called [INAUDIBLE], which was a jail.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they put them there until they were resettled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They actually didn't want to put them in jail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't think so, because they were freed one by one after they found a place where they should stay.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But what happened the next couple of days, we had about 10 to 20 suicides daily in the ghetto by these people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They just didn't want to live anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They didn't want to live any more indignity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And about a week later, I was in the cemetery, and some of these bodies showed up.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
